{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01EWTE5aRc75VAE2jhCS5JZn","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tests pass. Here's a summary of the changes:\n\n**1. `release-task` host workflow** (`.cloche/host.cloche`) — New workflow definition with a single `release-task` step that runs the release script.\n\n**2. `release-task.sh` script** (`.cloche/scripts/release-task.sh`) — Runs `bd update $CLOCHE_TASK_ID -s open` to return the ticket to open status and unassign the owner.\n\n**3. Stale claim detection** (`internal/adapters/grpc/server.go`) — `GetLoopTasks` now checks active runs for each in-progress task. If a task has `in_progress` status but no active (pending/running) run, it's marked as `Stale: true`.\n\n**4. `ReleaseTask` method** (`internal/adapters/grpc/server.go`) — Runs the `release-task` host workflow for a given task ID.\n\n**5. `TaskEntry.Stale` field** (`internal/adapters/web/handler.go`) — New `stale` JSON field on `TaskEntry`. `TaskProvider` interface extended with `ReleaseTask(ctx, projectDir, taskID)`.\n\n**6. Release API endpoint** (`internal/adapters/web/handler.go`) — `POST /api/projects/{name}/tasks/{taskId}/release` calls `ReleaseTask` on the task provider.\n\n**7. Project view UI** (`internal/adapters/web/templates/project_detail.html`) — Tasks split into two panels:\n  - **In-progress Tasks** — shows `in_progress`/`in-progress` tasks with a **Release** button on stale ones\n  - **Upcoming Tasks** — shows `open` tasks (ready work queue)\n\n**8. Tests** — Updated existing mock, added tests for release endpoint (success, no provider, error), stale field serialization, and updated the panel structure test.\n\nCLOCHE_RESULT:success"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":358,"cache_read_input_tokens":97834,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":358},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard"